description: T.J.’s Dawg House is delivering Dallas the most delicious meaty dishes. They serve up only the very best ¼ pound Vienna Beef to ensure that your hot dog is top dog. You’ll find all the classics on their amazing mobile menu....You can go for the Chicago Style and “drag it through the garden” (top it with Relish, Onions, Sport Peppers, Tomato, & Pickle), the Beantown Dog (with Boston Baked Beans & Melted Cheddar Cheese), or The Chef’s Choice (topped with Chili & Sauerkraut) - just to name a few. For an authentic dog that’s so tasty it’ll just make your doggone day, you’ll have to make your way over to T.J.’s Dawg House today!
name: T.J.'s Dawg House
